Class BigdataNativeServiceOptions

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INativeServiceOptions, IServiceOptions

    public class BigdataNativeServiceOptions
extends ServiceOptionsBase
implements INativeServiceOptions
    Service options base class for bigdata aware services. Such services are expected to interchange IBindingSets containing IVs. The IVs are NOT guaranteed to be materialized.
